Package provided.jxMaps.utils.enhanced

"Enhanced" subclasses of MapObject entities that add additional functionality or bug fixes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnhancedCircle
    An extension of com.teamdev.jxmaps.Circle that adds additional functionality.
    EnhancedInfoWindow
    An InfoWindow with enhanced capabilities, especially in terms of fixing the issue with InfoWindow where it needs to be both instantiated with a map and issued its open() methods with a map.
    EnhancedMarker
    A Marker subclass that adds additional functionality
    EnhancedPolygon
    A subclass of Polygon that adds additional functionality and transparently fixes a bug in its use of its PolygonOptions where IllegalArgument (unsupported parameter) exception in Polygon.setOptions(options) if the paths were set in the PolygonOptions.
    EnhancedPolyline
    A subclass of Polyline that adds additional functionality
    EnhancedRectangle
    An extension of com.teamdev.jxmaps.Rectangle that adds additional functionality.
